{"tid":1373092,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府將於星期一下半旗致哀 悼念李鵬","createTime":"2019-07-27T14:33:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T20:12:21.000Z","uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":156,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"c62fbd664028f1d62eaf5164ab00043d064dd855","tid":1373092,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:33:16.000Z","msg":"下半旗誌哀<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n按照中央人民政府通知，香港特別行政區政府將於星期一（七月二十九日）於添馬政府總部及禮賓府下半旗（包含國旗和區旗），以悼念已故國務院原總理、前全國人民代表大會常務委員會委員長李鵬。 <br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2019年7月27日（星期六）<br />\n香港時間22時15分"},{"pid":"ecb5848d91b37a5b7aba9e5cb7a55f5b3a06284c","tid":1373092,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:33:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201907/27/P2019072700955.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201907%2F27%2FP2019072700955.htm&d=%2FFjBtsZQ5cEfgjMY%2Bqoz3nr2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=7a54b038\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201907/27/P2019072700955.htm</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab641a7c2b3a888c8576ff9e71bd8dc342f0a140","tid":1373092,"uid":259901,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:35:24.000Z","msg":"殺人放火金腰帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"661856acdde94648a1a1a018f1d36892ded456dc","tid":1373092,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:35:31.000Z","msg":"澳門都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1470850-20190727.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1470850-20190727.htm&d=%2FFjBtsZQ5cEfgjMY%2Bqoz3nr2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=28241706\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http